T1  - Winning the second race of technology standardization: Strategic maneuvers in SEP follow-on innovations
AU  - Yao, Li
AU  - Li, Jun
AU  - Chen, Kaihua
AU  - Yu, Rongjian
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 53
IS  - 6
SP  - 105023
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/07/01/
